[{"id":"FT543045","type":"longtextV2","stimulusHtml":"<p>The four pictures present a story. Imagine you are writing the story to a friend. Narrate a complete story as suggested by the pictures. Give your story a beginning, a middle, and an end.&nbsp;Type your response in the target language.</p>\n\n<p><img alt=\"Four pictures are shown in a square grid to present a story.   Picture 1 is in the upper left corner. A woman wearing a backpack is standing next to a baggage carousel with a concerned expression. One red suitcase is on the carousel. A thought bubble above her shows a large light blue suitcase, a smaller purple suitcase, and a small purple bag.  Picture 2 is in the upper right corner. The woman is standing in a bedroom and her backpack is leaning against the leg of the bed. The closet is empty and there are no sheets on the bed. The medicine cabinet in the bathroom can also be seen, and it is open and empty.   Picture 3 is in the lower left corner. The woman is opening her front door and three people are standing outside smiling. One woman is holding a garment bag, another is holding a bag of groceries, and a man is holding a pile of folded sheets and blankets.   Picture 4 is in the lower right corner. The woman is holding the front door open and a delivery man with a clipboard is putting the two suitcases and smaller bag from her thought bubble inside.\" height=\"357\" src=\"https://assets.learnosity.com/organisations/537/media.academicmerit.com/586f076e1d9638837c0dee0298aa7988/original.jpg\" width=\"355\" /></p>\n","features":[{"type":"sharedpassage","html":"<p>You will be asked to perform two writing tasks in Chinese. In each case, you will be asked to write for a specific purpose and to a specific person. You should write in as complete and as culturally appropriate a manner as possible, taking into account the purpose and the person described.</p>"}]}]